<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenue chez {{companyName}} - Votre partenaire financier moderne</title>
    <style>
        /* Style Global */
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .header {
            background-color: {{companyPrimaryColor}};
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle, {{companyPrimaryColor}} 10%, {{companySecondaryColor}} 90%);
        }

        .header img {
            width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .hero {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 0;
            color: {{companyPrimaryColor}};
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .content ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .content li {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .content li span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content a {
            color: {{companyPrimaryColor}};
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: {{companyPrimaryColor}};
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: {{companySecondaryColor}};
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #888;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: {{companyPrimaryColor}};
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: {{companyTertiaryColor}};
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 5px solid {{companyPrimaryColor}};
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .social-links {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .social-links a {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{templateCampaignImg}}" alt="{{companyName}} Logo">
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Bienvenue chez {{companyName}}</h1>
            <p>Votre partenaire financier de confiance</p>
            <a href="{{ctaLink}}" class="button">Commencez dès maintenant</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Nous sommes heureux de vous compter parmi nous. Voici vos informations de connexion :</p>
            <ul>
                <li><span>Nom d'utilisateur :</span> {{username}}</li>
                <li><span>Mot de passe :</span> {{name}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Pour toute question ou assistance, contactez-nous à <a href="mailto:{{CompanyLink}}">{{CompanyLink}}</a> ou appelez-nous au <a href="tel:{{companyPhone}}">{{companyPhone}}</a>.</p>
            <p>Suivez-nous également sur nos réseaux sociaux :</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Links Section -->
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="{{companyLinkFb}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
            <a href="{{companyLinkTwit}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
            <a href="{{companyLinkInsta}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="{{companyLinkTiktok}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-tiktok"></i></a>
            <a href="{{companyYoutube}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-youtube"></i></a>
            <a href="{{companyPinterest}}" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i></a>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. Tous droits réservés.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
